🚨 Loads kya karta hai? (from https://youtu.be/Nc8au-99pfI?t=66)
loads koi bhi json jaisi string ko ek python dict mein convert kar deta hai.
..
loads string ko convert kar deta hai object mein & vo object hoti hai Python ki dictionary.

🚨 dumps kya karta hai? (from https://youtu.be/Nc8au-99pfI?t=174)
dumps ek python dict ko json string mein convert kar deta hai.
..
koi bhi python object/dict usko agar string mein convert karna hai to dumps use karna hoga.

🧠 json to dict k liye json.loads() use hota hai. 
 OR in other words
🧠 with json.loads 'json string' will be converted to python dict.

🧠 with json.dumps python dict will be converted to json string.

practice this till the concept is clear : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJeKgpjbQYc